      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a superlative example of the S65 high-revving V8 era. Featuring a 4.0L naturally aspirated powerplant with an 8,400 RPM redline, this unit has undergone meticulous preventative maintenance, including VAC-coated rod bearings and upgraded throttle actuators. The chassis remains taut with original EDC (Electronic Damping Control) functionality and a perfectly indexed M-Variable limited-slip differential. The exterior retains its factory depth with zero oxidation on the shadowline trim, ensuring the vehicle maintains its original aerodynamic profile and torsional rigidity. A true collector-grade specimen for the discerning purist demanding linear power delivery and mechanical perfection.",
